node.text:
The Bella’s are back… for a good cause!
 
There’s nothing perfect about the world we’re living in. Families around the globe are suffering from the impact of the #COVID19 pandemic, especially those in Lebanon who are facing crisis after crisis. But we can all pitch in and help. 
 
The proceeds from the downloads & streams of our rendition of “Love on Top” will go to @UNICEF to help children in Lebanon and around the world who need our support right now.
 
Click the link in my bio for more.  #ForEveryChild #Beirut #COVID19

node.title: Bella’s Are Back 💕 Love On Top

node.text:
I. Can’t. Believe. It’s. Been. 4. Years. 
This song has changed my life in ways I didn’t think were possible. This song has given me so much strength and comfort in times of self doubt. This song has taken me to some of the most beautiful places around the world. This song has introduced me to so many of you.

I hope Love Myself has helped you realize how special you really are. ❤️ In celebration, please enjoy this video of little baby Haiz on the set of her very first music video ever. I love you guys. THANK YOU for your endless support. 
More coming SO very soon....
